data.SysSock.Use: "off") # Turn off message reception via local log socket;
data.StateFile: "/run/log/imjournal.state") # File to store the position in the journal

data.certs: $dir/certs# Where the issued certs are kept
data.crl_dir: $dir/crl# Where the issued crl are kept
data.x509_extensions: usr_cert# The extensions to add to the cert
data.default_md: default# use public key default MD
data.crypto_device: builtin# OpenSSL engine to use for signing
data.default_policy: tsa_policy1# Policy if request did not specify it
data.digests: sha1, sha256, sha384, sha512  # Acceptable message digests (mandatory)
data.ordering: yes# Is ordering defined for timestamps?
data.tsa_name: yes# Must the TSA name be included in the reply?
data.ess_cert_id_chain: no# Must the ESS cert id chain be included?
